name: HaikuChef
0:
”Alexa, open haiku chef”
”Alexa, ask haiku chef to cook a haiku for me”
”Alexa, ask haiku chef to tell us a poem”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: haiku chef
des:
Haiku Chef reads out loud random haikus that all have some reference to food. Funny or philosophical, these selected haikus will never leave you indifferent.
All you have to do is to ask Haiku Chef to tell or rather to "cook" a haiku for you, and your mood appetite will be satisfied.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
